<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="About PixelNest - Empowering creators with AI technology">
    <title>About Us - PixelNest</title>
    
    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/img/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/img/favicon.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/img/favicon.png">
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
    <script src="/js/theme-manager.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="text-white">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <main class="mt-20">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="section-container relative z-10">
                <div class="text-center mb-16">
                    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 glass rounded-full text-xs font-mono font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 text-violet-400">
                        About Us
                    </span>
                    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">
                        Empowering Creativity<br/>with AI Technology
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                        We're on a mission to democratize content creation by making powerful AI tools accessible to everyone.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Mission & Vision -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600 to-fuchsia-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">Our Mission</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            To empower creators, businesses, and individuals with cutting-edge AI technology that transforms ideas into stunning visual content. We believe creativity should have no boundaries, and technology should amplify human imagination, not replace it.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">Our Vision</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            To become the leading AI-powered creative platform in Southeast Asia, where anyone can bring their creative visions to life instantly. We envision a future where AI tools are as accessible as smartphones, enabling unprecedented creative freedom.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Story -->
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">Our Story</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            <p>
                                PixelNest was born from a simple observation: content creation was too expensive, too slow, and too complicated for most people and businesses. Traditional methods required specialized skills, expensive equipment, and countless hours of work.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Founded in 2024 in Pringgasela, Lombok Timur, we set out to change that. Starting with a small team of AI enthusiasts and creative professionals, we built a platform that combines the power of cutting-edge AI models with an intuitive, user-friendly interface.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Today, PixelNest serves thousands of creators, businesses, and agencies across Indonesia, helping them generate millions of images and videos. From solo entrepreneurs to large enterprises, our users are pushing the boundaries of what's possible with AI-powered creativity.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                But we're just getting started. Our team continues to innovate, bringing new AI models, features, and capabilities to our platform every month. We're committed to staying at the forefront of AI technology while keeping our platform accessible and affordable for everyone.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Values -->
                <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center mb-12 tracking-tight">Our Values</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚀</div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-violet-400">Innovation First</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">We constantly push boundaries and embrace emerging AI technologies to deliver the best tools.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🤝</div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-fuchsia-400">User-Centric</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Our users' success is our success. Every feature is designed with their needs in mind.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💎</div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-blue-400">Quality & Reliability</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">We deliver consistent, high-quality results that our users can depend on every time.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌍</div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-purple-400">Accessibility</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Advanced AI should be affordable and easy to use for everyone, regardless of technical skills.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Stats -->
                <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-16">
                    <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center mb-12 tracking-tight">PixelNest by the Numbers</h2>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-4xl font-black gradient-text mb-2">2.5M+</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Generations</div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-4xl font-black gradient-text mb-2">10K+</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Active Users</div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-4xl font-black gradient-text mb-2">50+</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">AI Models</div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-4xl font-black gradient-text mb-2">99.9%</div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Uptime</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Team -->
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center mb-12 tracking-tight">Our Leadership Team</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600 to-fuchsia-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
                                👨‍💼
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Ahmad Ridwan</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-violet-400 mb-2">CEO & Founder</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Former AI Engineer at Tech Giant</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-600 to-pink-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
                                👩‍💻
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Siti Nurhaliza</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-fuchsia-400 mb-2">CTO</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">ML Specialist & System Architect</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
                                👨‍🎨
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Budi Santoso</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-blue-400 mb-2">Head of Product</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Creative Director & UX Expert</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contact -->
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="glass-strong rounded-2xl p-12 text-center">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight">Join Our Journey</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">PixelNest Headquarters</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Jln Pendidikan Pringgasela, Lombok Timur, Nusa Tenggara Barat, 83665</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary px-8 py-3">Get in Touch</a>
                            <a href="/auth/register" class="btn-outline px-8 py-3">Start Creating</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

